Feature: Comprehensive Analysis and Specification

  Scenario: Analyze and specify requirements based on provided context
    Given the requirements are incomplete or missing
    And the previous analysis indicates a lack of necessary details
    When the user provides the necessary details and context
    Then perform a comprehensive analysis of the provided information
    And create a detailed technical design specification
    And ensure all requirements are clearly defined and documented
    And validate the specification with the user for accuracy and completeness
